WEBVTT

00:11.690 --> 00:17.820
[July 24, 00:18]

00:17.930 --> 00:20.530
[Huang Song]

00:29.830 --> 00:30.360
Cheng...

00:30.760 --> 00:31.320
Cheng.

00:31.760 --> 00:33.390
Meng Ling has been shot dead.

00:33.880 --> 00:34.810
What did you say?

00:35.110 --> 00:37.350
Meng Ling was shot dead.

00:38.560 --> 00:40.070
Shot dead? What do you mean?

00:40.070 --> 00:41.430
Lai has a gun.

00:41.750 --> 00:43.960
He shot and killed Meng Ling.

00:44.920 --> 00:46.450
Meng Ling wanted to go home,

00:46.710 --> 00:48.790
and she tried to blackmail him
with the leverage she had on him.

00:48.790 --> 00:50.640
So he shot her dead.

00:51.430 --> 00:52.230
Where are you?

00:52.750 --> 00:53.710
We're by...

00:53.710 --> 00:54.920
We are by the Tong River.

00:54.920 --> 00:56.350
How come you can call me?

00:56.470 --> 00:57.800
I'm in the car right now.

00:58.000 --> 00:59.070
He can't see me.

00:59.600 --> 01:00.430
Y-Y-You...

01:00.430 --> 01:01.670
Please, save me,

01:01.670 --> 01:02.390
Cheng.

01:03.150 --> 01:04.280
Please save me.

01:04.510 --> 01:05.760
He's almost here.

01:06.590 --> 01:08.000
Is he going to kill me?

01:08.510 --> 01:09.640
Save me...

01:10.510 --> 01:12.120
Calm the hell down!

01:20.730 --> 01:21.500
Do as I say.

01:21.920 --> 01:23.400
First, just follow Lai San.

01:23.400 --> 01:24.150
Tell him—

01:24.480 --> 01:25.840
under no circumstances should he
even think about dismembering the body,

01:25.840 --> 01:26.510
let alone run.

01:26.510 --> 01:28.120
Otherwise, the police
will get there faster.

01:28.120 --> 01:28.710
Got it?

01:29.870 --> 01:31.200
Are you listening to me?

01:31.560 --> 01:33.289
I'm listening. I'm listening.

01:35.100 --> 01:36.030
Keep an eye on your surroundings.

01:36.030 --> 01:37.430
Don't let anyone see you.

01:41.640 --> 01:43.000
The rain probably won't stop,

01:43.000 --> 01:44.350
so there won't be much blood left behind.

01:44.350 --> 01:45.229
Huang Song, listen carefully.

01:45.229 --> 01:46.920
Don't help him with anything else.

01:46.920 --> 01:48.000
Just tell Lai San—

01:48.039 --> 01:48.950
the more he does,

01:48.950 --> 01:50.840
the more clues the police will find.

01:50.840 --> 01:51.950
Just throw the body in the water.

01:51.950 --> 01:52.680
Understand?

01:53.039 --> 01:53.840
I understand.

01:55.070 --> 01:56.229
Whose car are you driving?

01:56.229 --> 01:56.950
Lai's.

01:57.150 --> 01:58.400
Is the dashcam on?

01:59.560 --> 02:00.280
As soon as he fired the gun,

02:00.280 --> 02:01.530
I pulled the card out.

02:01.640 --> 02:02.770
Hide the card first.

02:02.920 --> 02:03.950
Don't let Lai San find out.

02:03.950 --> 02:04.350
Okay.

02:04.710 --> 02:05.440
I'll just...

02:05.640 --> 02:06.840
I'll just throw the card into the river.

02:06.840 --> 02:09.639
If you don't want to be done for,
do exactly as I say.

02:10.750 --> 02:11.280
Got it.

02:11.750 --> 02:12.870
I understand.

04:03.090 --> 04:09.090
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

04:09.420 --> 04:11.750
[Episode 5]

04:14.960 --> 04:16.160
I want to see Huang Song's

04:16.160 --> 04:17.560
past record

04:17.720 --> 04:19.209
and his family background.

04:19.209 --> 04:19.730
Sure.

04:19.760 --> 04:20.490
That's easy—

04:21.000 --> 04:23.330
we did a thorough check
before the interrogation.

04:23.330 --> 04:25.390
Hold on, please. Let me get it for you.

04:27.270 --> 04:28.480
Huang Song's previous records

04:28.480 --> 04:29.560
are mostly for fights and brawls,

04:29.560 --> 04:30.680
nothing serious.

04:31.120 --> 04:33.360
His family background is fairly simple—

04:33.360 --> 04:34.000
he's from a single-parent household

04:34.000 --> 04:35.390
and lives with his mother.

04:35.390 --> 04:35.950
However,

04:36.120 --> 04:38.510
about 6 months ago,
his mother was diagnosed with uremia.

04:38.510 --> 04:40.710
Her condition doesn't look promising,

04:40.800 --> 04:43.210
and she's currently hospitalized
at the Municipal People's Hospital.

04:43.210 --> 04:43.810
By the way,

04:43.840 --> 04:45.440
I'll send you his file later.

04:47.790 --> 04:50.360
Does his mother know
about his current situation?

04:50.360 --> 04:50.920
No.

04:51.270 --> 04:52.950
Huang Song is quite devoted
to his mother.

04:52.950 --> 04:54.480
He even requested the team

04:54.720 --> 04:55.850
not to notify the family—

04:55.850 --> 04:58.090
probably afraid it would upset her.

07:20.780 --> 07:24.760
[Ward]

07:42.600 --> 07:43.370
You are...

07:44.040 --> 07:44.840
Hello, ma'am.

07:45.310 --> 07:46.510
My last name is Jiang.

07:50.780 --> 07:52.040
This is my official ID.

07:54.120 --> 07:55.180
Please take a seat.

08:10.630 --> 08:11.560
I'm here

08:11.970 --> 08:13.200
about a situation

08:13.230 --> 08:14.600
concerning your son, Huang Song.

08:14.600 --> 08:17.930
I want to get a little more information
about his situation.

08:18.270 --> 08:20.930
I've been trying to call him
these past few days,

08:21.630 --> 08:22.960
but he hasn't answered.

08:23.060 --> 08:24.290
Now his phone is off.

08:25.480 --> 08:26.880
Has something happened?

08:27.470 --> 08:28.800
He's involved in a case.

08:29.360 --> 08:30.600
Is he okay?

08:30.710 --> 08:31.310
He's fine,

08:31.950 --> 08:33.679
and he's at the police station.

08:34.409 --> 08:36.799
Then he must have
gotten into trouble again.

08:36.799 --> 08:37.600
Is it serious?

08:38.980 --> 08:40.770
The case is still under investigation,

08:40.770 --> 08:41.830
so I can't say much.

08:43.760 --> 08:45.150
Just tell me clearly—

08:45.670 --> 08:47.330
what did he do wrong this time?

08:47.750 --> 08:48.870
Will he be detained?

08:48.870 --> 08:49.600
For how long?

08:51.150 --> 08:52.290
It's a homicide case,

08:52.290 --> 08:53.800
but he's not the perpetrator.

08:53.800 --> 08:54.930
That's all I can say.

09:00.060 --> 09:01.460
It's all my fault...

09:03.360 --> 09:05.090
I didn't raise him properly...

09:06.160 --> 09:06.760
Back then,

09:07.910 --> 09:08.510
his father

09:08.870 --> 09:09.630
left us

09:09.870 --> 09:11.000
and walked away.

09:13.780 --> 09:15.110
I was afraid to remarry,

09:15.670 --> 09:17.870
fearing someone would treat him badly.

09:18.400 --> 09:20.920
So I raised him on my own—the whole time.

09:22.960 --> 09:24.150
It's all my fault...

09:25.770 --> 09:27.930
I haven't even given him

09:28.010 --> 09:29.810
a proper meal most of the time...

09:35.000 --> 09:36.260
Everyone has to grow up

09:37.040 --> 09:39.680
and take responsibility
for their own actions.

09:39.680 --> 09:40.850
That's true,

09:41.670 --> 09:43.660
but I still feel guilty about him.

09:48.180 --> 09:49.180
If you don't mind,

09:49.670 --> 09:50.930
I have a few questions.

09:51.680 --> 09:52.280
Go ahead.

09:53.040 --> 09:54.440
According to the police,

09:54.720 --> 09:57.120
your financial situation isn't very good.

09:57.180 --> 09:57.930
Normally,

09:58.670 --> 10:00.060
you wouldn't be able to afford

10:00.060 --> 10:01.660
this level of hospital care.

10:04.050 --> 10:05.860
I was transferred not long ago.

10:06.440 --> 10:08.210
Before that, I had always

10:08.250 --> 10:09.650
been in the regular ward.

10:10.190 --> 10:11.720
When were you transferred?

10:12.740 --> 10:15.290
I think it was on the 24th or 25th.

10:17.160 --> 10:18.620
Did Huang Song arrange it?

10:20.960 --> 10:22.410
How could he?

10:24.320 --> 10:26.320
I was lucky to meet a living saint.

10:27.790 --> 10:28.390
He said

10:28.390 --> 10:29.600
his company

10:29.790 --> 10:31.390
was doing charity work.

10:32.200 --> 10:34.440
When he saw my condition
worsening rapidly,

10:34.440 --> 10:35.960
he decided to include me

10:35.960 --> 10:37.200
in a new drug trial.

10:38.290 --> 10:41.350
He also promised to actively help me
find a kidney donor

10:41.440 --> 10:43.240
and cover the associated costs.

10:45.030 --> 10:46.080
Can you be more specific?

10:46.080 --> 10:47.740
For example, what's his name?

10:50.200 --> 10:51.930
I'm not really sure about that.

10:53.030 --> 10:54.360
He never told me,

10:54.870 --> 10:56.670
and he never allowed questions.

10:57.280 --> 10:59.380
I think he just wants

10:59.440 --> 11:01.100
to do good deeds anonymously.

11:03.030 --> 11:03.910
He came by

11:04.670 --> 11:06.070
just before you arrived.

11:37.670 --> 11:42.880
[2002]

11:39.550 --> 11:41.880
Jiang Hansheng, what's going on with you?

11:42.240 --> 11:43.900
You just don't like me, do you?

11:46.320 --> 11:48.430
[Young Jiang Hansheng]

11:49.330 --> 11:51.730
[Young Jiang Cheng]

12:42.080 --> 12:43.080
I recognize you—

12:44.180 --> 12:45.930
the Pup from No. 23 Zhizi Alley.

12:48.840 --> 12:50.240
Long time no see.

12:53.930 --> 12:55.660
That was your doing, wasn't it?

12:56.660 --> 12:57.700
What did I do?

12:58.790 --> 13:00.590
You got Lai Zhengtian locked up.

13:03.930 --> 13:05.860
You really think I'm that capable?

13:07.660 --> 13:08.860
It wasn't difficult.

13:09.600 --> 13:10.720
You used a kid—

13:11.670 --> 13:12.460
Huang Song.

13:19.600 --> 13:21.530
Meng Ling's death was unexpected,

13:21.710 --> 13:23.340
but the way the body was disposed of...

13:23.340 --> 13:25.070
it was meticulous and careful.

13:25.360 --> 13:26.550
The police never managed

13:26.550 --> 13:28.350
to find the primary crime scene.

13:28.720 --> 13:30.550
That shows the person
in charge of the disposal

13:30.550 --> 13:32.010
was completely composed,

13:32.470 --> 13:34.910
with exceptional anti-detection skills.

13:36.000 --> 13:38.000
We're not at the stage
of talking about this, are we?

13:38.000 --> 13:38.670
Huang Song is just

13:38.670 --> 13:40.620
an immature kid.

13:41.750 --> 13:43.010
But you're different.

13:44.000 --> 13:45.200
I admit it—

13:45.900 --> 13:47.310
you're imaginative.

13:48.030 --> 13:50.560
But police investigations
rely on evidence.

13:50.600 --> 13:51.790
Do you have any?

13:55.390 --> 13:56.440
No.

13:57.030 --> 13:58.690
No wonder they call you "Pup."

13:58.960 --> 14:01.220
You really can go after whoever you want.

14:01.360 --> 14:02.890
You want me dead that badly?

14:03.360 --> 14:04.620
I've thought about it.

14:06.630 --> 14:07.870
Well, too bad for you.

14:08.430 --> 14:10.470
I don't have much in my favor

14:10.720 --> 14:11.750
except my luck.

14:20.270 --> 14:21.600
Let's cut the crap.

14:22.030 --> 14:23.510
I warned you before,

14:23.510 --> 14:25.080
and I'll say it again:

14:26.120 --> 14:27.150
stay away from me.

14:29.870 --> 14:31.870
You don't have the right to say that.

14:32.670 --> 14:34.470
You're a scumbag with no limits.

15:55.960 --> 15:57.620
Just like Huang Song's house,

15:57.660 --> 15:59.660
there wasn't a single abnormality,

16:00.010 --> 16:02.670
let alone evidence
to implicate Lai Zhengtian.

16:03.250 --> 16:05.510
Everything had already been cleaned up.

16:10.840 --> 16:13.510
Cheng even advised her
to go back to school,

16:12.540 --> 16:16.540
[As long as one is willing,
it's never too late.]

16:13.910 --> 16:14.790
telling her

16:15.540 --> 16:17.000
that as long as she is willing,

16:17.000 --> 16:18.390
it's never too late.

16:21.750 --> 16:22.300
Senior,

16:23.140 --> 16:24.130
Chief Tan sent a message

16:24.130 --> 16:25.310
saying that if we can't find it,
we should head back first.

16:25.310 --> 16:26.460
Today we're going
to do the crime scene walkthrough.

16:26.460 --> 16:26.990
Let's go.

16:29.240 --> 16:29.770
Let's go.

16:30.190 --> 16:31.020
There's still one more person

16:31.020 --> 16:32.350
we must question today.

16:34.190 --> 16:35.190
Who is it, Senior?

16:35.840 --> 16:36.370
Who is it?

16:53.880 --> 16:55.850
You really never take a break, do you?

16:55.850 --> 16:57.240
I have some questions for you.

16:57.240 --> 16:57.790
Get lost.

16:58.010 --> 16:59.270
What's that attitude?

16:59.400 --> 17:00.330
Watch your tone.

17:02.010 --> 17:04.010
Before Meng Ling met Lai Zhengtian,

17:04.630 --> 17:06.430
did she ever say anything to you?

17:06.760 --> 17:08.490
You were the person she trusted most,

17:08.490 --> 17:10.020
so you must know something.

17:10.800 --> 17:11.640
You don't have to admit

17:11.640 --> 17:13.240
your relationship with her.

17:14.440 --> 17:16.369
Don't you want to know
how she died?

17:16.930 --> 17:17.780
Or do you

17:19.359 --> 17:20.819
already know everything?

17:21.359 --> 17:22.359
I had nothing to do

17:22.920 --> 17:23.849
with Meng Ling.

17:23.940 --> 17:25.140
That's not the point.

17:25.290 --> 17:26.550
Meng Ling said she had a hold

17:26.550 --> 17:28.109
over Lai Zhengtian.

17:28.450 --> 17:30.060
I want you to tell me honestly—

17:30.060 --> 17:31.350
what exactly

17:31.570 --> 17:32.520
did she have,

17:32.880 --> 17:33.740
and where is it?

17:34.750 --> 17:36.680
Why should I help you investigate?

17:36.990 --> 17:38.850
Why don't you go ask your husband?

17:41.430 --> 17:42.360
Jin,

17:42.890 --> 17:44.550
I really underestimated you—

17:44.810 --> 17:45.870
you've got a talent

17:45.880 --> 17:46.810
for luring guys.

17:49.990 --> 17:51.120
Keep your distance.

17:52.720 --> 17:54.070
Don't change the subject.

17:54.070 --> 17:55.070
Just answer me—

17:55.670 --> 17:56.970
what exactly did Meng Ling know?

17:56.970 --> 17:57.700
I don't know.

17:57.750 --> 17:59.810
And even if I did, I wouldn't tell you.

18:00.640 --> 18:01.470
Jiang Cheng,

18:02.160 --> 18:03.780
you are obliged to cooperate
with our investigation.

18:03.780 --> 18:04.330
Cheng.

18:05.070 --> 18:05.640
Cheng,

18:06.080 --> 18:07.010
what's going on?

18:08.700 --> 18:09.990
You're not welcome here.

18:09.990 --> 18:10.910
If you want to search,

18:10.910 --> 18:11.840
bring a warrant.

18:13.500 --> 18:14.360
Close the door.

18:24.640 --> 18:25.200
Senior,

18:26.680 --> 18:29.130
what exactly is your relationship
with him?

18:29.130 --> 18:30.320
I can't shake the feeling

18:30.320 --> 18:31.720
that he knows something.

18:32.970 --> 18:35.100
Does Professor Jiang know about this?

18:38.730 --> 18:40.460
Does Chief Tan know about this?

18:42.440 --> 18:45.770
Let's take Huang Song
to the crime scene walkthrough first.

18:50.550 --> 18:52.880
So... what is your relationship, really?

18:54.310 --> 18:54.880
Cheng.

18:55.270 --> 18:56.530
That idiot just now...

18:59.570 --> 19:00.830
You should rest first.

19:24.100 --> 19:30.210
[July 23, 21:45]

19:33.110 --> 19:33.680
Cheng.

20:03.880 --> 20:05.740
Did you call me here just for this?

20:09.680 --> 20:10.540
Can't I do this?

20:11.170 --> 20:11.720
No.

20:14.160 --> 20:15.110
Why not?

20:28.050 --> 20:29.250
Why won't you want me?

20:30.920 --> 20:32.030
Didn't you say

20:32.650 --> 20:33.710
that you're my man?

20:45.110 --> 20:45.680
Cheng,

20:47.610 --> 20:49.410
you know I have feelings for you.

20:50.760 --> 20:52.760
I've actually been waiting for you.

20:53.710 --> 20:54.990
As long as you want me,

20:57.030 --> 20:59.400
I'll go along with whatever life
we end up with.

20:59.400 --> 21:00.530
I'll stay with you
for the rest of my life.

21:00.530 --> 21:01.160
Meng Ling,

21:03.200 --> 21:04.200
don't be so silly.

21:13.160 --> 21:14.560
Do you think I'm tainted?

21:21.790 --> 21:23.110
What right do I have

21:23.760 --> 21:25.160
to think you're tainted?

21:29.970 --> 21:30.530
Alright.

21:30.930 --> 21:32.790
Just don't act like this anymore.

21:39.590 --> 21:40.270
Wait.

22:03.070 --> 22:04.310
This is my amulet.

22:11.350 --> 22:13.350
Your amulet doesn't look like much.

22:13.910 --> 22:16.600
You have to take good care
of the things I give you.

22:16.600 --> 22:18.000
Don't ever throw it away.

22:19.400 --> 22:20.060
Promise me.

22:24.830 --> 22:25.400
Okay,

22:26.220 --> 22:27.030
I promise you.

22:31.590 --> 22:32.240
You can deny

22:32.240 --> 22:33.830
your relationship with Meng Ling
all you want.

22:33.830 --> 22:35.160
But don't you want to know

22:35.160 --> 22:36.030
how she died?

22:37.280 --> 22:39.010
Don't you care about her at all?

22:59.440 --> 23:01.100
They were arguing right here.

23:02.120 --> 23:03.780
Where was your car at the time?

23:04.000 --> 23:05.880
It was probably around
where the police car is now.

23:05.880 --> 23:07.340
Where's the dashcam card?

23:07.370 --> 23:08.570
Where did you hide it?

23:08.630 --> 23:09.590
Under the rock.

23:26.270 --> 23:26.880
Is this it?

23:29.300 --> 23:30.730
Huang Song,

23:31.110 --> 23:32.880
you dare to betray me?

23:32.900 --> 23:34.540
I treated you so well,

23:34.570 --> 23:37.000
yet you betray me!

23:41.810 --> 23:43.670
Lai Zhengtian, let me remind you:

23:43.810 --> 23:45.610
you still have a chance right now

23:46.590 --> 23:48.270
to make up for your crimes.

23:49.030 --> 23:50.360
Tell me where the gun is.

23:51.830 --> 23:52.680
Where did you

23:52.880 --> 23:54.030
get the gun?

23:54.640 --> 23:56.040
How did you contact them?

23:56.960 --> 23:58.160
I'll say it again—

23:58.880 --> 24:01.440
actively cooperating
with the investigation

24:01.440 --> 24:04.500
will be an important factor
in how your case is handled.

24:10.610 --> 24:11.270
So, have you

24:13.720 --> 24:14.850
thought it through?

24:16.270 --> 24:18.200
I don't know what kind of gun it was.

24:18.820 --> 24:19.680
I just found it.

24:22.030 --> 24:22.920
Lai Zhengtian,

24:23.350 --> 24:25.010
you don't have many chances left.

24:25.010 --> 24:26.940
Think carefully before you speak.

24:58.790 --> 24:59.400
Cheng?

25:01.790 --> 25:02.400
Cheng?

25:03.420 --> 25:04.010
Come in.

25:04.320 --> 25:04.920
Cheng,

25:05.070 --> 25:06.000
Boss He is here.

25:10.120 --> 25:10.920
Cheng, Cheng,

25:11.860 --> 25:14.060
they even turned off the surveillance.

25:29.700 --> 25:30.100
Cheng!

25:30.110 --> 25:30.790
Cheng.

25:30.880 --> 25:31.550
Cheng!

25:31.640 --> 25:32.110
Don't move!

25:32.110 --> 25:32.470
Don't move!

25:32.470 --> 25:33.150
Crouch down!

25:33.150 --> 25:33.810
Don't move!

25:35.950 --> 25:36.610
Don't move!

25:37.330 --> 25:38.330
Crouch properly!

25:40.670 --> 25:41.240
Boss He,

25:43.000 --> 25:44.130
what does this mean?

25:56.320 --> 25:56.990
Cheng,

25:58.890 --> 26:00.290
you're not being honest.

26:03.880 --> 26:04.540
Don't move!

26:06.640 --> 26:08.880
Cheng.

26:16.050 --> 26:16.650
Stop hitting him!

26:16.650 --> 26:17.290
Liu Jinlong,

26:17.290 --> 26:19.620
if you've got the guts,
come at me instead!

26:21.240 --> 26:21.810
Enough.

26:48.750 --> 26:49.660
Cheng,

26:51.560 --> 26:53.360
I've always admired you.

26:56.410 --> 26:59.010
But you shouldn't have
bullied Lai Zhengtian.

26:59.490 --> 27:00.290
You know

27:01.480 --> 27:03.440
he's my cousin.

27:05.230 --> 27:06.030
It's true that

27:06.130 --> 27:07.330
he's a bit of a failure

27:07.580 --> 27:08.690
and a jerk.

27:09.120 --> 27:11.270
But he's related to me after all.

27:11.670 --> 27:13.230
My relatives asked me
to take good care of him,

27:13.230 --> 27:15.460
and now, you've gotten him
into the police station.

27:15.460 --> 27:17.860
How am I supposed to explain this
to anyone?

27:18.500 --> 27:19.900
I bullied Lai Zhengtian?

27:26.270 --> 27:27.070
That's right.

27:28.510 --> 27:30.640
If Lai Zhengtian weren't your cousin,

27:30.960 --> 27:32.760
I would have crippled him by now.

27:33.930 --> 27:34.730
Jiang Cheng,

27:35.240 --> 27:37.040
you're still playing dumb, huh?

27:37.220 --> 27:38.780
You'd better tell Boss He right now

27:38.780 --> 27:40.220
how you set up Lai!

27:40.390 --> 27:41.390
I'm talking to Boss He.

27:41.390 --> 27:42.450
Stop yapping, you!

27:43.300 --> 27:44.060
Are you...

28:00.700 --> 28:03.300
Now that everyone's here,
let's talk about it.

28:04.670 --> 28:05.530
Over the years,

28:06.250 --> 28:07.920
Lai Zhengtian has caused
so much trouble

28:07.920 --> 28:09.650
and ruined so many businesses.

28:09.670 --> 28:10.980
Everyone has seen it.

28:11.630 --> 28:12.190
Boss He,

28:12.950 --> 28:15.190
we follow you to make money,

28:15.460 --> 28:17.520
not to clean up Lai Zhengtian's mess.

28:17.850 --> 28:18.980
You say I framed him,

28:19.320 --> 28:21.580
but was it me who told him
to kill someone?

28:21.700 --> 28:24.430
Bleach is just a kid.
He was scared out of his wits.

28:24.430 --> 28:25.670
He knew I used to be a cop,

28:25.670 --> 28:26.670
so he came to ask me

28:26.700 --> 28:27.670
what to do.

28:28.630 --> 28:29.760
I told him what to do,

28:30.110 --> 28:30.950
and that's it.

28:32.100 --> 28:33.430
So what did you tell him?

28:34.740 --> 28:35.630
I told him

28:35.660 --> 28:36.910
how to handle the body

28:37.060 --> 28:38.960
and how to avoid the police investigation.

28:38.960 --> 28:39.520
Boss He,

28:39.650 --> 28:40.510
I can vouch for it,

28:40.510 --> 28:41.310
as I was there.

28:41.430 --> 28:43.020
Cheng was really trying to help Lai.

28:43.020 --> 28:44.190
Help him with what?

28:44.390 --> 28:44.870
Where is Lai then?

28:44.870 --> 28:45.260
Where is he?

28:45.260 --> 28:46.110
Where is Lai now?

28:46.110 --> 28:47.910
I wasn't helping Lai Zhengtian,

28:51.260 --> 28:52.350
I was helping you,

28:52.700 --> 28:53.260
Boss He.

28:56.870 --> 28:59.070
Boss He, have you heard of the 8.17 Case?

28:59.580 --> 29:00.380
Yes, I have.

29:00.870 --> 29:01.950
Once the shooting happened,

29:01.950 --> 29:03.950
arresting people was a minor issue.

29:04.110 --> 29:05.010
Where's the gun?

29:05.010 --> 29:05.840
Where did it come from?

29:05.840 --> 29:06.970
That's the big deal.

29:07.390 --> 29:08.430
Lai San is nobody.

29:09.110 --> 29:10.470
But who does he represent
behind the scenes,

29:10.470 --> 29:12.130
and where will this fire lead?

29:12.560 --> 29:13.120
Boss He,

29:13.770 --> 29:15.200
do I need to keep going?

29:17.700 --> 29:19.590
I, Jiang Cheng, didn't get to

29:19.830 --> 29:21.350
where I am today just for the money—

29:21.350 --> 29:22.290
I also sought loyalty.

29:22.290 --> 29:23.610
When I was in prison,

29:23.740 --> 29:25.660
your brother, He Wen,
treated me the best.

29:25.660 --> 29:27.590
When he was bullied in there,

29:27.770 --> 29:29.060
I took the beatings for him.

29:29.060 --> 29:30.150
I even got stabbed in the lower back

29:30.150 --> 29:31.500
protecting him.

29:31.500 --> 29:32.540
You know all this.

29:32.980 --> 29:34.090
When I got out of prison,

29:34.090 --> 29:35.070
the police didn't want me,

29:35.070 --> 29:36.130
and no one wanted me.

29:36.130 --> 29:37.460
It was you who took me in,

29:37.740 --> 29:38.540
gave me honor,

29:38.540 --> 29:39.350
and gave me a way out.

29:39.350 --> 29:41.080
I only remember your kindness,

29:41.780 --> 29:42.350
Boss He.

29:43.250 --> 29:44.450
If it weren't for you,

29:45.060 --> 29:46.990
I would've killed Lai San already.

29:48.670 --> 29:49.950
So, what do you think?

29:52.030 --> 29:54.230
Does Lai Zhengtian still have a way out?

29:58.350 --> 30:00.350
If the police hadn't found the body,

30:01.350 --> 30:03.220
it wouldn't have been his time to die.

30:03.220 --> 30:04.150
Too bad they did.

30:04.590 --> 30:05.590
But as long as

30:06.420 --> 30:07.830
he doesn't rat you out,

30:08.240 --> 30:10.040
we'll still respect him as a man.

30:11.260 --> 30:12.590
As for everything else,

30:13.870 --> 30:15.730
this is already the best outcome.

30:15.930 --> 30:16.490
Boss He,

30:16.740 --> 30:18.550
Cheng is actually right.

30:18.700 --> 30:19.550
Yes, Boss He,

30:19.700 --> 30:20.910
we all trust Cheng.

30:21.390 --> 30:23.200
He doesn't get along with Lai, but...

30:23.200 --> 30:24.460
-Shut up.
-But he never played dirty.

30:24.460 --> 30:25.720
That's right, Boss He.

30:26.040 --> 30:27.640
Are you all nuts?

30:27.770 --> 30:29.170
You want to call him boss?

30:30.460 --> 30:31.150
Cheng,

30:33.870 --> 30:35.130
you're quite popular.

30:36.980 --> 30:39.310
Boss He, you don't need
to drop hints to me.

30:39.500 --> 30:41.230
No one can wrongfully accuse me

30:41.390 --> 30:42.990
of something I haven't done.

30:43.390 --> 30:45.320
I don't need anyone to speak for me.

30:48.720 --> 30:49.380
Don't move!

30:55.560 --> 30:56.120
Boss He,

30:57.670 --> 30:59.470
you treat Lai San like a brother,

30:59.700 --> 31:01.830
and come all the way here
to stand up for him.

31:01.830 --> 31:03.690
But do you know how he treated you?

31:13.910 --> 31:15.780
Meng Ling was killed

31:16.380 --> 31:18.640
by Lai San because she filmed this video.

31:22.670 --> 31:23.220
Mr. Lin,

31:23.360 --> 31:24.220
all you need to do

31:24.220 --> 31:25.920
is affix your seal on that contract,

31:25.920 --> 31:27.060
and once the deal goes through,

31:27.060 --> 31:28.220
I'll give you 3 million.

31:28.220 --> 31:29.220
Well...

31:29.350 --> 31:30.880
Does Mr. He know about this?

31:30.910 --> 31:31.950
Well,

31:32.120 --> 31:33.800
at a certain age,

31:34.270 --> 31:36.270
people need to step aside

31:36.540 --> 31:38.870
and make room
for the younger generation.

31:39.060 --> 31:39.860
You're right.

31:40.460 --> 31:41.220
You've

31:41.510 --> 31:42.550
got ambition,

31:42.840 --> 31:43.390
and I

31:43.630 --> 31:45.600
like ambitious people.

31:45.980 --> 31:47.260
As for He Wu,

31:47.290 --> 31:48.050
he's always

31:48.460 --> 31:50.190
second-guessing everything.

31:50.670 --> 31:53.200
It's time for him to retire
and enjoy his life.

31:58.020 --> 31:58.590
Boss He,

32:01.060 --> 32:02.660
it's not just Lai Zhengtian.

32:03.700 --> 32:04.430
Liu Jinlong,

32:06.540 --> 32:08.220
do you know about this?

32:10.100 --> 32:10.740
I...

32:10.760 --> 32:12.020
I don't know anything.

32:12.590 --> 32:14.050
Jiang Cheng, listen to me.

32:14.330 --> 32:15.590
We've tolerated you

32:15.590 --> 32:16.380
taking people and turf,

32:16.380 --> 32:17.300
but you better not
mess with this nonsense

32:17.300 --> 32:18.260
or try to act all mysterious.

32:18.260 --> 32:18.740
I'm warning you.

32:18.740 --> 32:20.150
You've taken all
of Lai Zhengtian's shady contracts,

32:20.150 --> 32:21.830
his secret dealings,

32:21.830 --> 32:23.350
and his private funds, right?

32:23.350 --> 32:24.570
Tell me, is there any chance

32:24.570 --> 32:26.540
you're the one
who got Lai Zhengtian locked up?

32:26.540 --> 32:27.350
What the hell are you talking about?

32:27.350 --> 32:28.260
He's locked up,

32:28.290 --> 32:29.490
and you take over his position.

32:29.490 --> 32:30.540
Then you spread rumors

32:30.540 --> 32:31.900
saying I'm the one
who did it to Lai Zhengtian.

32:31.900 --> 32:32.910
Killing two birds with one stone.

32:32.910 --> 32:34.150
With that, you'll knock down two rivals.

32:34.150 --> 32:35.550
If you look at it that way,

32:36.300 --> 32:38.560
Liu Jinlong, your methods are ruthless.

32:39.590 --> 32:40.190
I don't...

32:40.190 --> 32:41.540
How could I, Boss He...

32:41.600 --> 32:42.120
I...

32:42.150 --> 32:43.150
I'm not that smart

32:43.220 --> 32:43.930
to plan all...

32:43.930 --> 32:44.590
all that...

32:46.780 --> 32:47.300
Cheng,

32:48.350 --> 32:50.410
you can fool around with other stuff,

32:52.150 --> 32:54.410
but you can't just say whatever you want.

32:54.550 --> 32:55.110
Boss He,

32:55.350 --> 32:56.810
I'm not talking nonsense.

32:57.390 --> 32:58.320
I have evidence.

33:21.870 --> 33:22.670
Sorry,

33:23.550 --> 33:25.210
I stole these from your place.

33:26.630 --> 33:27.500
Is this...

33:27.980 --> 33:28.640
a password?

33:28.870 --> 33:30.200
For Liu Jinlong's safe?

33:53.590 --> 33:55.390
You little bastard, I...

33:55.870 --> 33:57.190
I took a quick look

33:57.780 --> 33:58.980
at these accounts.

33:59.260 --> 34:00.980
You've done a pretty good job,
I'll admit.

34:00.980 --> 34:01.870
Honestly,

34:01.970 --> 34:03.110
I learned a thing or two

34:03.110 --> 34:04.700
about accounting
while I was in prison,

34:04.700 --> 34:06.260
and I have to say, I'm not on your level.

34:06.260 --> 34:07.830
This isn't just accounting,

34:07.830 --> 34:09.139
this is an art form.

34:09.580 --> 34:12.510
Perhaps you want
to explain this to Boss He yourself?

34:13.320 --> 34:14.719
Boss He, I...

34:14.980 --> 34:15.440
just...

34:15.790 --> 34:16.520
Liu Jinlong,

34:17.139 --> 34:18.179
I didn't expect it.

34:18.179 --> 34:19.980
After all these years with Lai San,

34:19.980 --> 34:21.340
you managed to hide it so well.

34:21.340 --> 34:22.500
You've taken all of this—

34:22.500 --> 34:24.580
do you think you can handle it
all by yourself?

34:24.580 --> 34:26.460
If I hadn't found out today,

34:26.460 --> 34:27.710
would we all

34:27.710 --> 34:29.370
have to call you Boss Liu soon?

34:39.929 --> 34:41.230
Xiao Mao, bring me a clean cloth.

34:41.230 --> 34:41.840
Yes.

34:51.909 --> 34:55.040
This is how you should handle
physical evidence. Got it?

34:55.199 --> 34:55.719
Boss He,

34:56.830 --> 34:58.830
here's the gun you were looking for.

35:01.230 --> 35:02.290
You take care of it.

35:03.270 --> 35:05.070
No one is allowed to use it again.

35:06.190 --> 35:06.920
Understood.

35:16.310 --> 35:17.060
Cheng,

35:18.310 --> 35:19.580
any more surprises?

35:21.500 --> 35:23.560
Boss He, if you ever stop trusting me,

35:24.390 --> 35:25.590
I can leave anytime.

35:26.310 --> 35:28.580
I had enough of feeling wronged
when I was in the police force.

35:28.580 --> 35:29.790
What I hate most now

35:29.790 --> 35:31.250
is being falsely accused.

35:34.790 --> 35:35.310
And

35:36.870 --> 35:37.980
from now on,

35:38.790 --> 35:40.500
I won't let any small-time nobody

35:40.500 --> 35:41.980
boss me around.

35:54.100 --> 35:54.950
Cheng,

35:56.950 --> 35:57.750
I really

35:59.390 --> 36:00.750
am getting on in years.

36:02.020 --> 36:03.280
I've lost my judgment.

36:04.580 --> 36:05.790
I owe you an apology

36:07.620 --> 36:08.460
for this.

36:11.060 --> 36:13.390
From now on,
the position of Lai Zhengtian

36:13.830 --> 36:14.620
is yours.

36:18.910 --> 36:20.430
Go treat that wound,

36:22.540 --> 36:25.200
and in a few days,
I'll introduce you to someone.

36:29.180 --> 36:30.580
You take care of all this.

36:31.230 --> 36:32.360
Take him back for me;

36:32.830 --> 36:34.430
I need to question him again.

36:39.500 --> 36:40.540
Cheng, Cheng...

36:40.540 --> 36:41.270
are you okay?

36:42.680 --> 36:43.950
Cheng! Cheng!

36:48.100 --> 36:49.500
The Meng Ling murder case

36:49.950 --> 36:50.950
is basically

36:51.620 --> 36:53.180
settled now.

36:53.950 --> 36:54.910
However,

36:55.500 --> 36:57.270
we've discovered
many more suspicious points.

36:57.270 --> 37:00.330
The larger case behind it
is still shrouded in mystery.

37:01.060 --> 37:03.060
which is still shrouded in mystery.

37:03.110 --> 37:05.880
So, given the current situation,

37:06.000 --> 37:07.600
the higher-ups have decided

37:08.630 --> 37:10.230
to make new arrangements

37:11.140 --> 37:13.270
for the investigation of the 8.17 Case.

37:13.270 --> 37:14.600
We're planning to bring

37:14.900 --> 37:17.270
in a former leader who is familiar
with the situation from back then

37:17.270 --> 37:19.180
to take the lead on cracking the case.

37:19.180 --> 37:20.240
Who is this person?

37:20.380 --> 37:21.690
Leader Yao is coming.

37:21.710 --> 37:23.600
It's Comrade Yao Weihai,
who was the leader

37:23.600 --> 37:26.350
of the task force for the 8.17 Case.

37:27.240 --> 37:28.730
He's now with the Provincial
Criminal Investigation Department.

37:28.730 --> 37:30.860
I hope everyone will cooperate fully.

37:31.020 --> 37:31.910
Yes, Sir.

37:33.750 --> 37:34.620
Senior,

37:35.790 --> 37:37.400
do you know Yao Weihai?

37:38.800 --> 37:39.650
No, I don't.

37:41.140 --> 37:42.920
Take on the responsibility, will you?

37:42.920 --> 37:43.890
Yes.

37:48.500 --> 37:49.140
Come in.

37:51.350 --> 37:51.870
Sir,

37:52.880 --> 37:53.810
you got a minute?

37:54.250 --> 37:55.060
Come on in.

37:55.180 --> 37:55.530
Okay.

38:02.020 --> 38:04.620
There are some things
I'd like to ask you about.

38:04.630 --> 38:05.460
Go ahead then.

38:06.580 --> 38:08.140
After Leader Yao arrives,

38:08.230 --> 38:09.830
will I still be able

38:09.860 --> 38:11.500
to participate in the investigation
like I am now?

38:11.500 --> 38:12.790
It's not up to me.

38:13.850 --> 38:14.970
But I think

38:15.490 --> 38:16.820
he might bring in people

38:17.460 --> 38:18.590
he's familiar with,

38:19.140 --> 38:21.070
people he has good chemistry with.

38:22.670 --> 38:26.000
The original team members
are all familiar with Leader Yao.

38:26.100 --> 38:27.810
I'm the one who came in halfway.

38:27.810 --> 38:28.540
That's true.

38:29.710 --> 38:32.100
But hey, don't spend all your time
worrying about this.

38:32.100 --> 38:33.230
Does that help with anything?

38:33.230 --> 38:34.160
You're a newbie.

38:34.430 --> 38:37.030
Just follow
whatever the higher-ups arrange.

38:42.350 --> 38:43.310
Hey,

38:43.910 --> 38:46.100
since you were transferred to the CIB,

38:47.310 --> 38:49.790
the Meng Ling case
is your first major case.

38:50.600 --> 38:52.180
The higher-ups are keeping a close eye

38:52.180 --> 38:54.750
on your performance.

38:55.190 --> 38:56.450
Don't worry, alright?

39:01.750 --> 39:03.210
It's mainly because of...

39:04.100 --> 39:05.020
Jiang Cheng.

39:05.540 --> 39:07.870
What does Jiang Cheng
have to do with this?

39:07.890 --> 39:09.140
I have a feeling.

39:09.230 --> 39:10.890
I'm not sure if it's accurate,

39:11.390 --> 39:13.520
but based on what I know of Jiang Cheng,

39:14.460 --> 39:15.660
I feel like he's

39:16.230 --> 39:17.630
not as simple as he seems.

39:20.870 --> 39:21.750
Yeah,

39:22.060 --> 39:23.520
he's definitely not simple.

39:23.520 --> 39:24.390
These days,

39:24.830 --> 39:26.010
everyone

39:26.750 --> 39:28.610
has a different version of Cheng.

39:30.020 --> 39:32.000
Someone who should have been a comrade

39:32.000 --> 39:35.140
has now become the most formidable enemy.

39:36.830 --> 39:37.830
So, do you think

39:38.020 --> 39:38.750
Leader Yao might

39:38.750 --> 39:40.550
take me off the case just because

39:41.950 --> 39:43.500
of my past connection with Jiang Cheng?

39:43.500 --> 39:45.560
What connection do you have with him?

39:45.750 --> 39:47.900
You don't have any connection with him.

39:47.900 --> 39:48.830
Let's not forget

39:49.140 --> 39:50.540
that you're married now.

39:50.920 --> 39:52.680
Time has passed, and things have changed,

39:52.680 --> 39:53.430
understand?

39:54.870 --> 39:56.310
Stop talking nonsense.

39:57.250 --> 39:58.170
Okay.

40:00.500 --> 40:01.350
By the way,

40:01.790 --> 40:04.590
why didn't Hansheng show up
for the meeting today?

40:04.600 --> 40:05.600
You're asking me?

40:05.980 --> 40:07.250
It's been the whole day,

40:07.250 --> 40:08.830
and I haven't heard a word from him.

40:08.830 --> 40:10.960
Well, if he hasn't contacted you,
why don't you send him a message?

40:10.960 --> 40:11.690
Hey,

40:12.430 --> 40:13.560
let me tell you this,

40:13.870 --> 40:16.200
I know you two rushed into marriage.

40:17.170 --> 40:19.210
But feelings need to be nurtured,

40:19.240 --> 40:20.300
do you understand?

40:20.540 --> 40:22.540
That kind of thing
isn't very common these days.

40:22.540 --> 40:22.790
No, I mean...

40:22.790 --> 40:24.350
But looking back, wasn't it always
the leaders who arranged things first?

40:24.350 --> 40:25.350
Afterwards, couples got married

40:25.350 --> 40:26.060
and worked on building their feelings.

40:26.060 --> 40:26.830
That's how feelings...

40:26.830 --> 40:28.760
I'll leave you to it. I'm going out.

40:28.900 --> 40:30.770
I'm talking about something important.

40:30.770 --> 40:32.060
I-I... I'll take care of it.

40:32.060 --> 40:32.790
I haven't...

40:59.830 --> 41:01.330
[What are you doing?]

41:11.100 --> 41:12.910
[Why didn't you come
to the meeting today?]

41:24.770 --> 41:26.420
[We have a meeting today.
Why didn't you come?]

41:30.790 --> 41:32.980
Zhou Jin, where did you

41:33.100 --> 41:34.300
put the wedding ring?

41:34.580 --> 41:36.870
Why are you asking about this
all of a sudden?

41:36.870 --> 41:37.670
It's nothing.

41:37.870 --> 41:39.870
Go ahead and carry on with your work.

41:48.620 --> 41:49.140
Dan,

41:49.790 --> 41:51.650
I want to take half a day off today.

41:52.430 --> 41:53.310
What for?

41:53.780 --> 41:55.980
I need to go back to my former apartment.

41:56.060 --> 41:58.190
I forgot to take something important.

41:58.220 --> 42:00.050
You haven't finished moving yet?

42:00.050 --> 42:01.510
I've been too busy lately.

42:01.800 --> 42:02.860
Alright, go ahead.

42:03.100 --> 42:04.390
If anything comes up, I'll call you.

42:04.390 --> 42:06.340
Alright, I'm leaving then.

42:11.910 --> 42:14.180
All the details regarding the assault
on Lai Zhengtian on Funing Street

42:14.180 --> 42:16.250
have been provided to Zhou Jin
of the Nancheng Branch.

42:16.250 --> 42:17.780
Her knowledge of the matter

42:18.280 --> 42:20.010
exceeds what is recorded here.

42:21.300 --> 42:23.430
Did the girl
who was hurt by Lai Zhengtian

42:23.430 --> 42:24.630
file a police report?

42:24.660 --> 42:25.430
She did,

42:25.460 --> 42:27.140
but there wasn't enough evidence
to open a case.

42:27.140 --> 42:28.310
Is there a record of the incident?

42:28.310 --> 42:28.910
Yes,

42:29.550 --> 42:30.880
let me look it up for you.

42:33.580 --> 42:35.970
This happened 5 or 6 years ago.

42:36.230 --> 42:39.120
Her brother probably couldn't get over it

42:39.500 --> 42:42.100
and decided to have someone
teach Lai Zhengtian a lesson.

42:42.100 --> 42:43.500
Fortunately, nothing serious happened.

42:43.500 --> 42:46.180
Otherwise, he would've gotten himself
into trouble too.

42:46.180 --> 42:46.790
Here it is.

42:55.180 --> 42:57.220
